          .titleText
            If you have Dropbox App already loaded on your iPad please touch the green "Allow" button to establish iDropCopy link.
          %br/
          %img{:alt => "Dropbox iDropCopy Allow", :border => "0", :src => "/img/help/ipad/idropcopy-dropbox-allow.png", :style => "vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:15px;"}/
