          If you
          %b do not
          have Dropbox App loaded on your iPad please sign in or touch the "New to Dropbox? Get the App!" link.
          %br/
          %img{:alt => "Dropbox iDropCopy Login", :border => "0", :src => "/img/help/ipad/idropcopy-ipad-dropbox-login.png", :style => "vertical-align:top;padding-top:15px;padding-bottom:10px;"}/
    
    